    <h1>Coffee, Chagga Culture, and the Slopes of Kilimanjaro</h1>
    <p>The Chagga people on the southern slopes of Mount Kilimanjaro, the coffee farms that define the lower mountain, and the Materuni waterfall day trip that brings it all together.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <span>By <a href="/about">Nelson Mushi</a></span>
      <span>&middot; 2026-06-14</span>
      <span>&middot; <a href="/blog">Back to Blog</a></span>
    </div>
  </div>
